<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Why Volunteer at Kiran Foundation?</title>
  <style>
    .frame {
      width: 100%;
      height: 366px;
      max-width: 1296px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .frame-heading {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 734px;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cards {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .card {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 300px;
      max-width: 370px;
      height: auto;
      padding: 20px;
      gap: 16px;
      border-radius: 36px;
      background: #E5F1FF;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .card img {
      width: 50px; 
      height: auto;
    }

    .d-flex {
      display: flex;
    }

    .align-items-center {
      align-items: center;
    }

    .mb-3 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .flex-shrink-0 {
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .rounded-1 {
      border-radius: 0.25rem;
    }

    .p-2 {
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }

    .fs-sm {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .cards {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .card {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: none;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="frame">
    <h2 class="frame-heading">Why Volunteer at Kiran Foundation?</h2>
    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 rounded-1 p-2">
            <img src="/assets/img/benefits/icon.png" alt="Image">
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="fs-sm" style="word-wrap: break-word;">To positively impact the lives of those most in need, join us in making a difference</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 rounded-1 p-2">
            <img src="/assets/img/benefits/icon.png" alt="Image">
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="fs-sm" style="word-wrap: break-word;">We offer a range of volunteering opportunities that fit your interests.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 rounded-1 p-2">
            <img src="/assets/img/benefits/icon.png" alt="Image">
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="fs-sm" style="word-wrap: break-word;">You, who want to break the mold and create a better tomorrow.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
